    <!--

    TO FIND ACCENT COLORS (except for Black colors):

    • xxxColorAccent: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°200
    • xxxColorPrimary: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°200
    • xxxPrimaryInverse: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°600
    • xxxPrimaryContainer: https://colorffy.com/color-scheme-generator :
        - Color: xxxPrimaryInverse
        - Mixing colors: Move the cursor to the end which makes 20 shades appear
        - Select the 10th shade
    • xxxOnPrimary: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°800
    • xxxSecondaryContainer: https://colordesigner.io/color-mixer
        - Choose only 2 colors
        - 1st color = xxxPrimaryInverse ==> Quantity 1
        - 2nd color = xxxColorSurface ==> Quantity 2
        - Select mixed color
    • xxxColorSurface: https://colorffy.com/dark-theme-generator :
        - Primary color: xxxColorAccent
        - Dark color: #000000
        - Mix Intensity: Move the cursor one notch
        - Select the color where it is written: "Mixed - a20"
    • xxxColorBackground: https://colorffy.com/dark-theme-generator :
        - Primary color: xxxColorAccent
        - Dark color: #000000
        - Mix Intensity: Leave the cursor at the 1st position
        - Select the color where it is written: "Mixed - a0"

    -->

